# Google Sign-In (optional). Get a Client ID from Google Cloud Console:
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Create or select a project → APIs & Services → Credentials
# 3. Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application)
# 4. Add authorized JavaScript origins (e.g. http://localhost:5173, your production URL)
# 5. Copy the Client ID here (no quotes).
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
